thread.title: Catherine

author: Catherine
title: Catherine
text: At first I was hesitant about signing up but when I saw u basically got 2 months for the price of one I felt like they were generally interested in helping me find a room-mate - and it worked! It took roughly 40 days, but I have found a wonderful fellow to share with my nephew and myself, and I couldn't be happier with how easy the website was to use and navigate. Thank you!
